sourcesContent:
const testimonials = [
    {
      id: 1,
      name: "Agnes Remi",
      role: "Back-end Developer at MyDodow",
      review:
        "Dico is finally addressing a long-time problem we had when building UIs. Its ease of use and workflow seem really intuitive. Promising!",
      date: "2021.03.02",
      avatar: "/images/avatar1.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      name: "John Carter",
      role: "Full-Stack Developer at CodeSphere",
      review:
        "The framework is lightweight and makes API integrations seamless. A game-changer for web and mobile app development!",
      date: "2022.05.10",
      avatar: "/images/avatar2.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      name: "Sophia Lee",
      role: "React Native Developer at Appify",
      review:
        "Developing cross-platform apps has never been this smooth. The performance improvements are remarkable!",
      date: "2023.01.15",
      avatar: "/images/avatar3.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 4,
      name: "David Kim",
      role: "Software Engineer at DevWorks",
      review:
        "The UI components are well-structured and customizable. My productivity in web development has skyrocketed!",
      date: "2023.06.07",
      avatar: "/images/avatar4.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 5,
      name: "Emma Wilson",
      role: "Mobile App Designer at NexaApps",
      review:
        "Finally, a tool that understands the real challenges of UI/UX design in mobile apps. It's intuitive and powerful!",
      date: "2022.09.21",
      avatar: "/images/avatar5.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 6,
      name: "Oliver Brown",
      role: "Tech Lead at CloudNest",
      review:
        "Great documentation and strong community support. It's becoming my go-to solution for modern web applications!",
      date: "2024.02.04",
      avatar: "/images/avatar6.jpg",
    },
    {
      id: 7,
      name: "Liam Davis",
      role: "Front-end Developer at PixelCraft",
      review:
        "I appreciate the attention to detail in accessibility features. This makes UI development much more inclusive and efficient.",
      date: "2023.11.29",
      avatar: "/images/avatar7.jpg",
    },
  ];
  
  export default testimonials;
